fko.chessly.player.computer.Omega

Class OmegaTranspositionTable

  • java.lang.Object
    • fko.chessly.player.computer.Omega.OmegaTranspositionTable

  • public class OmegaTranspositionTable
extends java.lang.Object
    A cache for node results during AlphaBeta search. Implementation uses a simple array of an Entry class. The array indexes are calculated by using the modulo of the max number of entries from the key. entries[key%maxNumberOfEntries]. As long as key is randomly distributed this works just fine.
